     <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9" id="content-body">
      <section aria-labelledby="section-1-heading" id="section-1">
       <h2 class="section-heading sr-only" id="section-1-heading">
        <span>
         Section 1
        </span>
       </h2>
       <div class="row">
        <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-12">
         <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
          <pre class="h4 h5 h6 h2 h3"><span>New:</span><span> Please go to the </span><span>Financial Functions &amp; Procedures tab</span><span> above for instructions and information on new forms and procedures.</span></pre>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </section>
      <section aria-labelledby="section-2-heading" id="section-2">
       <h2 class="section-heading sr-only" id="section-2-heading">
        <span>
         Section 2
        </span>
       </h2>
       <div class="row">
        <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-3">
         <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
          <h3>
           History
          </h3>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-9">
         <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
          <p>
           <span>
            The Student Life &amp; Leadership Business Services Office (BSO) was established in July 2001 to support excellent business practice in accordance with UCI Policies and Procedures within the Office of the Dean of Students and Student Life &amp; Leadership. A central financial office was needed to facilitate budgetary, personnel actions, purchasing, and contract services on a departmental level.  A close collaboration between business managers, unit directors, coordinators, and satellite personnel was essential to swiftly expedite programmatic goals with financial back up and expertise.
           </span>
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="row">
        <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-3">
         <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
          <h3>
           <strong>
            What We Do
           </strong>
          </h3>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-9">
         <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
          <p>
           BSO researches solutions to meet the needs and service expectations of our faculty, staff and students while strictly adhering to the UCI Policy and Procedures directives. The office has a history of encouraging campus co-sponsorship and collaboration in order to present quality programs of interest to the diverse student population of UCI and to promote the higher education experience.
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="row">
        <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-3">
         <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
          <h3>
           Our Mission
          </h3>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-9">
         <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
          <p>
           <span>
            We are committed to maintaining campus environmental integrity, mutual respect and civility in the process of managing, and expediting financial projects.
           </span>
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </section>
     </div>
