       <strong>
        Business Meetings/Entertainment Reminder
       </strong>
       <br/>
       When submitting a list of attendees for catering events please include the name of host for event. Any event involving payment for food should include everyone who attended the event. Please
       <a href="https://cascade.content.uci.edu/entity/open.act?type=page&amp;id=aef3443080c8a8b6056cf4f9347fd034&amp;confId=0b2b64b980c8a8b677f37d138b83cd37" target="_parent">
        contact us
       </a>
       if you have any questions.
      </p>
      <hr style="width: 1px;" width="1"/>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Important W-2 Information
       </strong>
       <br/>
       To print a duplicate Form W-2:
      </p>
      <ol>
       <li>
        Log in to
        <a href="https://atyourserviceonline.ucop.edu/ayso/">
         At Your Service
        </a>
       </li>
       <li>
        Select the W-2 option located in Income and Taxes
       </li>
       <li>
        Print your W-2 (2013 is currently available online)
       </li>
       <li>
        <a href="https://portal.uci.edu/uPortal/f/welcome/p/webproxy-cms-file-view.u20l1n201/max/render.uP?pP_cmsUri=public%2FAccounting%2FPayroll%2FChecklistUnderstandingFormW2.xml" title="Understanding Your W-2">
         Understanding Your W-2 and more
        </a>
       </li>
      </ol>
